          "field_name": "promotional_period_text",
          "candidate_value": "How will I receive my tax slips for my EQ Bank RRSP? Tax slips, such as the RRSP Contribution Receipt or T4RSP, can be downloaded as PDFs by signing in to your account through the EQ Bank mobile app or web browser. You can find the dates of when these documents will be available ",
